    "href": "https://github.com/eliben/pycparser"
  }, "pycparser"), "."), mdx("p", null, "We can actually take this parsing approach one step further.  We can use the\nC/C++ parsers to translate source code into C-level declarations in pxd files\nand then use Cython's own parser to translate from pxd files into pyx files.  This\nlatter step is the approach taken by the ", mdx("a", {
